      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Looking at how the test works, and seeing that it creates transactions sending random recipient amounts up to the full balance, it seems likely that it occasionally creates some tiny UTXOs that are skipped during AvailableCoins(â¦) due to having a negative effective value. Since line 448 where this error occurs is trying to empty the wallet, using `sendall` seems like the appropriate fix. IIRC, we also allow creating a PSBT with `sendall`, so it would work for both 444 and 448. Might be an \"Easy first issue\"?",
